sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant Integration as TaijiVerifyIntegration
    participant Engine as TaijiVerifyEngine
    participant Embedding as EmbeddingProvider
    participant Polaris as PolarisCompiler
    participant DeltaS as ΔS Calculator
    participant BBMC as 坤守 BBMC
    participant BBPF as 乾进 BBPF
    participant BBCR as 复归 BBCR
    participant BBAM as 巽调 BBAM
    participant Observe as 观变 GuanObserve
    participant Detector as FailureModeDetector

    Note over User,Detector: ========== 完整推理循环 (TaijiVerifyEngine.step) ==========

    User->>Integration: 用户输入 (自然语言)
    Integration->>Integration: pre_process hook

    Integration->>Polaris: compile_goal(user_input)
    Polaris->>Polaris: Step 1: GOAL_COMPILATION
    Polaris->>Polaris: Step 2: TASK_GRAPH
    Polaris->>Polaris: Step 3: ATOM_TABLE
    Polaris-->>Integration: GoalCompilation + TaskGraph

    Integration->>Embedding: embed(user_input)
    Embedding-->>Integration: I (嵌入向量)

    alt 无预存目标G
        Integration->>Embedding: embed(goal_from_compilation)
        Embedding-->>Integration: G (目标嵌入)
    end

    Integration->>Engine: step(user_input, context)

    Note over Engine,Detector: ---------- 主循环迭代 ----------

    loop 每步推理
        Engine->>DeltaS: calculate_delta_s(I, G)
        DeltaS->>DeltaS: cos(I, G) → ΔS = 1 - cos
        DeltaS->>DeltaS: 锚点扩展 (if anchors exist)
        DeltaS->>DeltaS: 闸区判定 (safe/transit/risk/danger)
        DeltaS-->>Engine: DeltaSResult

        Engine->>Observe: record_snapshot(ΔS, round_id)
        Observe-->>Engine: GuanObserveSnapshot

        Engine->>BBMC: kun_guard(I, G, context_tokens)
        BBMC->>BBMC: m = cos(I, G)
        BBMC->>BBMC: c = clip(context/100, 0.2, 1.5)
        BBMC->>BBMC: B = I - G + m*c²
        BBMC->>BBMC: norm_B = ‖B‖₂
        BBMC->>BBMC: hazard判定 + 残差投影最小化
        BBMC-->>Engine: KunGuardResult

        alt hazard == COLLAPSE OR λ == chaotic
            Engine->>BBCR: fu_return(engine_state)
            BBCR->>BBCR: Phase 1: COLLAPSE (记录崩溃点)
            BBCR->>BBCR: Phase 2: RESET (回溯convergent节点)
            BBCR->>BBCR: Phase 3: REBIRTH (S_anchor+G)/2
            BBCR-->>Engine: FuReturnResult
            Engine->>Engine: I = new_state, 重新开始循环
        end

        Engine->>Engine: compute_lambda(ΔS_t, ΔS_t-1, history)
        Engine-->>Engine: λ状态 (convergent/recursive/divergent/chaotic)

        Engine->>BBPF: qian_advance(I, G, ΔS_prev, ΔS_now)
        BBPF->>BBPF: Phase 1: 耦合器W_c计算
        BBPF->>BBPF: Phase 2: k_paths 多路径扰动
        BBPF->>BBPF: Phase 3: f_S = 1/(1+mean(Δ))
        BBPF->>BBPF: Phase 4: 桥接判定
        BBPF-->>Engine: QianAdvanceResult

        alt bridge_enabled
            Engine->>Engine: 选用最优候选路径
        end

        Engine->>BBAM: xun_tune(attention_scores, W_c)
        BBAM->>BBAM: σ(a) → gate_factor = exp(-γ*σ)
        BBAM->>BBAM: α_blend = clip(0.50 + k_c*tanh(W_c), 0.35, 0.65)
        BBAM->>BBAM: 注意力混合 + softmax归一化
        BBAM-->>Engine: XunTuneResult

        Engine->>Detector: detect_all(state)
        Detector->>Detector: 运行16种失败模式检测
        Detector-->>Engine: List~FailureDetection~

        alt 检测到失败模式
            Engine->>Engine: 执行修复动作
            Engine->>Observe: record_failure(failure)
        end

        Engine->>Polaris: audit_downstream_leak(output, round_lock)
        Polaris->>Polaris: 检查输出类型匹配
        Polaris-->>Engine: DownstreamLeakAuditResult

        alt Leak Detected
            Engine->>Engine: 回合失败, 移除泄漏内容
            Engine->>Polaris: 重新执行(仅合法输出)
        end

        Engine->>Engine: I = select_best_candidate(candidates)
        Engine->>Engine: 更新 TaijiEngineState
        Engine->>Observe: record_state(state)
    end

    Note over Engine,Detector: ---------- 循环结束 ----------

    Engine->>Polaris: record_closure(atom_results)
    Polaris-->>Engine: ClosureRecord

    Engine-->>Integration: step结果 (ΔS, λ, 动作, 输出)

    Integration->>Integration: post_process hook

    alt passed
        Integration-->>User: 最终输出
    else 需降级
        Integration->>Integration: on_error fallback
        Integration-->>User: 降级输出 / 请求澄清
    end
